@ChatGPT genereted

## ⚙️ Tech stack

| What | Why |
|------|-----|
| **Tailwind CSS 3.4** | utility‑first styling, JIT purge, arbitrary values |
| **Node / npm** | single‑cli build with no bundler overhead |
| (optional) **GitHub Actions** | build & deploy to Pages in ~5 s |

---

## 🚀 Quick‑start

```bash
# 1 clone
git clone https://github.com/HTML-Kurz/TailwindCSS.git
cd TailwindCSS

# 2 install dependencies
npm i          # or npm install

# 3 dev mode: Tailwind watch + local server
npm run dev         # opens http://localhost:5173

# Terminal A – compile Tailwind continuously
npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./public/assets/css/style.css --watch

# Terminal B – serve /public
npx serve public         # default http://localhost:3000

start-landing
├─ node_modules/            # dependencies installed by npm; ignored by Git
├─ public/
│  ├─ assets/
│  │  └─ css/style.css      # generated by Tailwind; ignored by Git
│  └─ index.html
├─ src/
│  └─ input.css             # Tailwind directives + custom layers
├─ tailwind.config.js
├─ package.json
└─ .gitignore

